{"id":984335345,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"5 months, 1 week","timestamp":1688279978,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"9 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/984335345/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"String to Integer (atoi)","memory":"7 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int myAtoi(string s) {\n        int n=s.size(),idx=0;\n        double num=0;\n        bool positive=true;\n        while(idx<n)\n        if(s[idx]==' ') idx++;\n        else break;\n        if(s[idx]=='-' || s[idx]=='+'){\n            positive=s[idx]=='-'?false:positive;\n            idx++;\n        }\n        while(idx<n){\n            if(s[idx]<='9' && s[idx]>='0')\n            num=(num*10)+(s[idx]-'0');\n            else break;\n            idx++;\n        }\n        if(!positive) num*=(-1);\n        if(num>INT_MAX) return(INT_MAX);\n        if(num<INT_MIN) return(INT_MIN);\n        return((int)num);\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"string-to-integer-atoi","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
